        <item>
            <title>Elon Musk 正創造世界最強 AI     使用 10 萬個 Nvidia GPU 訓練 Gork-3</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/elonmusk-builds-most-powerful-ai-in-the-world/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=elonmusk-builds-most-powerful-ai-in-the-world</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/elonmusk-builds-most-powerful-ai-in-the-world/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:30:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Elon Musk]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Gork-3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[xAI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1252286</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Elon Musk 旗下的人工智能公司 xAI 計劃在年尾之前推出聲稱各項性能都是世上最強的人工智能，將使用 10 萬個液冷 H100 GPU 組成孟菲斯超級叢集（Memphis Supercluster），並用來訓練預計會在年尾推出的 Gork-3。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Glad to be making history with <a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@elonmusk</a>, such a great experience to work with his Memphis team! To meet the target, our execution had to be as perfect as possible, as quick as possible, as efficient as possible and as environmentally friendly as possible – lots of hard work, but…</p><p>&mdash; Charles Liang (@charlesliang) <a href="https://twitter.com/charlesliang/status/1815410868433428504?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">July 22, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">xAI 的第一款大模型 Gork-1 於 2023 年 11 月登場，Elon Musk 本月曾宣佈會在 8 月推出 Gork-2，如今再透露會使用 10 萬個 Nvidia H100 GPU 來訓練年尾推出的 Gork-3。這次項目與 Supermicro 合作，後者為 xAI 提供了大部份的硬件，而 Supermicro CEO Charles Liang 亦在 Elon Musk 的推文下留言高度讚場 xAI 團隊的執行能力。</p><p>由 10 萬個液冷 H100 GPU 組成的孟菲斯超級叢集，相信 GPU 性能上將能輕鬆超越最新 500 強上的任何東西。至於世界上最強大的超級電腦如 Frontier（37888 個 AMD GPU）、Aurora（60000 個 Intel GPU）和 Microsoft Eagle（14400 個 Nvidia H100 GPU）似乎都會被 xAI 大大拋離。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.tomshardware.com/pc-components/gpus/elon-musk-fires-up-the-most-powerful-ai-training-cluster-in-the-world-uses-100000-nvidia-h100-gpus-on-a-single-fabric">Tom’s Hardware</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://electrek.co/2024/06/04/elon-musk-asked-nvidia-prioritize-gpu-shipments-x-over-tesla-emails/">Electrek</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/tesla-to-have-humanoid-robots-for-internal-use-next-year/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla 人形機械人   Elon Musk 確認明年試產供內部使用</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/elon-musks-grok-chatbot-keeps-hallucinating-wrong-news/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">藉特朗普遭槍擊「創作」假新聞   Elon Musk 旗下 xAI 大型語言模型被狠批</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/elon-musk-21/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Elon Musk 爆料數月內曾被暗殺 2 次    「全力支持特朗普希望他早日康復」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/elonmusk-builds-most-powerful-ai-in-the-world/ai/">Elon Musk 正創造世界最強 AI     使用 10 萬個 Nvidia GPU 訓練 Gork-3</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
