        <item>
            <title>現實版《沙丘瀚戰》太空衣，可收集尿液並淨化成飲用水</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/dune-stillsuit-in-real-life/life-tech/health/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dune-stillsuit-in-real-life</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/dune-stillsuit-in-real-life/life-tech/health/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:00:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影視娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[DUNE]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[太空衣]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[沙丘瀚戰]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1252344</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">在 Frank Herbert 的科幻電影《沙丘瀚戰》（Dune）中，居住在沙漠星球的居民會穿著一種名為「Stillsuit」的先進服裝，能收集並循環利用人體的水分。有科學家受電影啟發，正研究同樣能將太空員尿液回收成飲用水的太空衣。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252349 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lowres_frontiersspac-466x580.jpg" alt="" width="466" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lowres_frontiersspac-466x580.jpg 466w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lowres_frontiersspac.jpg 563w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 466px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252350 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/astronautdiapermag-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/astronautdiapermag-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/astronautdiapermag.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252351 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lowres_frontiersspac-1-594x580.jpg" alt="" width="594" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lowres_frontiersspac-1-594x580.jpg 594w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lowres_frontiersspac-1.jpg 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 594px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://www.zmescience.com/space/space-flight-space/real-life-dune-suit-could-help-astronauts-conserve-water/">ZME Science</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">目前太空員的太空衣會配備一個名為 MAG （最大吸水性服裝）的東西，原則上是更先進的尿布，來處理太空員的尿液。MAG 被太空員長期抱怨缺乏舒適度和衞生，有機會令太空人受感染。威爾康奈爾醫學院最近的研究得到了突破性的進展，有望改善太空員的衞生、健康和執行任務的效率。他們設計出一個尿液收集裝置，會將尿液吸到收集杯內並由真空泵吸走。收集的尿液會輸送到尿液循環系統，分離尿液中的水分，再將水和鹽分分離。淨化後的水富豐富電解質，將會吸到飲用袋中供再次飲用。整個收集尿液並淨化成飲用水的過程只需 5 分鐘。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252354 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/maximumabsorbencygar-694x328.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="328" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/maximumabsorbencygar-694x328.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/maximumabsorbencygar.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252355 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/rearviewofurinerecyc-550x580.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/rearviewofurinerecyc-550x580.jpg 550w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/rearviewofurinerecyc.jpg 854w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 550px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/no-longer-science-fiction-scientists-develop-real-life-stillsuit-from-dune/">SciTechDaily</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">目前這個研究已經有原型可以使用，並正嘗試在現實環境中測試，希望盡快能夠應用在太空任務中。這個系統將在模擬的微重力環境下測試，因為微重力為研究的關鍵空間條件，測試將確保系統在實際太空任務中的功能性和安全性。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.zmescience.com/space/space-flight-space/real-life-dune-suit-could-help-astronauts-conserve-water/">ZME Science</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">圖片來源：<a href="https://gamerant.com/dune-stillsuit-explained/">Game Rant</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/dune-stillsuit-in-real-life/life-tech/health/">現實版《沙丘瀚戰》太空衣，可收集尿液並淨化成飲用水</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
